                        <div class="pricing-price" style="font-size:2.2em">¥69<span style="font-size:.4em;color:var(--dim)">/场</span></div>
                        <p style="color:var(--dim);font-size:.85em;margin-bottom:16px">常规对阵，标准分析</p>
                        <ul class="pricing-features">
                            <li>完整量化分析报告</li>
